Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說又發生了？ 這是連續殺人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們又死不了 所以一點實感都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是反而令人更加感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經掛了多少人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候真心求放過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銷量也受到影響了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的聖誕節就這麼泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 為什麼衛兵沒有出動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛兵是這個世界還是遊戲時候的治安系統
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能馬上察覺到戰鬥禁止區域的戰鬥行為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以瞬間移動前往鎮壓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們有著從外部大幅增加身體能力的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動力甲冑 Movable Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此 身為大地人的衛兵擁有超越冒險者的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使其維持治安成為可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就是聖誕夜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來是的 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前無異常情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始前往下一個區域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是說隨便就能找到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是什麼任務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說有點冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先看下他的屬性確認身份 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全滅？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的公會裡也都算高手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經超過十人遇害了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是恩巴特奈魯雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所屬公會 職業武士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,94級
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到的情報只有這點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 知道這麼多卻沒辦法行動才是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟就算被殺了 也不會就那麼完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們冒險者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬆散雖然也不是很好 不過總比混亂要好點嗎……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能早點解決的話 也就再也談不了什麼安穩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為也有考慮避難這個選項了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說要離開秋葉原嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是緊急手段而已 暫時移居涉谷之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先這就不是我們在場的人能決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 等級低的人先去避難比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點確實可以商討一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在秋葉原竟然有連續殺人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想點辦法制止才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說腹黑眼鏡現在在幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在他自己創立的議會上連續缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…他稍微有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說是為了攢錢在四處奔波呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟都臘月了 明天的聖誕節活動也是大頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:38.10,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(450,450)}*師走：日本對於12月的舊稱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贊德裡芙？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.50,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(450,450)}*遊戲地名，贊德裡芙大河
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓50級以下的人參加對地精殘當的討伐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下了這樣的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是應對殺人魔採取的避難措施的藉口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然本意上是如此喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不要那種特殊待遇 班長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我們也能……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬彌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想打倒殺人魔喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步不好就會死的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就有覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為還能復活嗎喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬彌親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為肉盾職業的心理準備如何啊喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你說那啊…… 一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,股腦衝上去直接死了是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊伍配合…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅僅是這樣喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復活本身就可以說是一種特殊待遇喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當你習慣了 我總覺得如果把這當作理所當然的事情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而會失去些什麼喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉 今天也沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38\an3}都到平安夜了 你們要跟我去吃個飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪……？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38\an2\pos(1073,710)}我來請
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺人鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟是些多餘的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38\an2\pos(1013,710)}平安夜還沒活動簡直不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38\an2\pos(1013,710)}什麼殺人鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主君會生氣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟在做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能保護蕾妮希雅公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我從什麼中保護她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說大地人很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她已經足夠強大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擁有保護她的資格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連去說點什麼的資格都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想變強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人很強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不能掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請記住對方的實力要超過大家 甚至我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要按班行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時進行報告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與主力部隊的聯絡由薺來擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果與目標進入交戰狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就採用甲種陣型的拖延戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次編隊所有班都配有2個治療
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻擊力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任務只是拖延和聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那麼宗次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要說的話她已經全替我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只說一句
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標是砍了自己人的魂淡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多也可以讓我上陣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想找殺人魔報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是才死過復活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一陣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗大人明明為我出頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管自己人中誰被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗次是絕對不會原諒對方的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗大人他對什麼女孩都很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是至少讓我有點幻想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在聖誕節喝豬骨湯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還放了鮭魚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實很溫柔啊 宗次他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他也不是什麼善良的好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是單純的是那樣的少年罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一旦生起氣來就不知道會做出什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那種和恐怖只隔了一張紙的溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候如果那兩個人在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能勸告宗次並影響他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只有一彥和城惠兩個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我想正月的時候一定能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還無法得知殺人魔的去向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在繼續巡邏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了曉也很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 城前輩也多加小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是出現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓調查班撤下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我們主力部隊來包圍殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾妮希雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,供贄一族的堇星大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼突然在大半夜前來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天冒然來訪真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為出了重要的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此來向蕾妮希雅大人說明和謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道衛士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒險者之間好像習慣把他們稱作衛兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他們對維護街區治安很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他們的屯所裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一套動力盔甲被偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被偷走的是一名衛兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據推測是我們供贄一族的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛士的動力盔甲時刻需要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從都市地下築造的巨大魔方陣中接受魔力補給
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據都市不同調整也會相異
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說即使帶出城也沒有意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反過來說就是如果在城內的話 它的力量是無法比擬的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的戰鬥能力都能夠超越冒險者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說殺人魔是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個罪行牽扯著供贄一族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我慚愧也只能得出這種結論
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說大地人殺害了冒險者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事是我們管理不周
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在供贄一族那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說 你們不能想想辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 蕾妮希雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 停止魔力供應的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動力甲冑就會失去功能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但與此同時 城市的防禦魔法陣也會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法防止怪物的入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再…再啟動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能立刻再次啟動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要花費以十年為單位的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能如此回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我沒聽到就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是被我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我聽到了又能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能保護蕾妮希雅公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不行了 真的不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼偏偏是現在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼偏偏是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏挑我前赴任的這時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能再想想辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再給點優惠服務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能手下留情一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去和圓桌會議商量一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那樣做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會和冒險者們產生衝突嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 但是也不能一直閉口不提
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是得說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個妖怪 為什麼偏偏挑這種時候不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的時候明明出現率高得讓人想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:14:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉斯提殿他 去了七瀑城寨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:14:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(805,670)}Seven'sHole
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就算這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說這些！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我擅自跑了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…你都聽到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好甜…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 吃甜的能讓人安心下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 畢竟世界並沒有那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人是大地人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會被偷？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷它的人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說他的目的和行蹤都還不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想潛伏地應該是下水道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為會失去戰鬥能力 所以並沒有出城的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去搜查他的地方就被限定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有全部搜到 不用如人耳目的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有下水道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 逮捕他的可能性也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 因為衛兵能夠瞬間移動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以即使包圍了他也能夠逃開…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘦小的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明肩負著重責
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻一直以這樣瘦小的肩膀 一直努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得煩惱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找出他來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去完成我的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我看到了你努力的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MT交換
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直繼 拉住仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧祭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往這邊看過來 大傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局長！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下 勇海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明承受了不少攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HP卻根本不見少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狀態欄也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 明明打成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛兵卻還不到場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是局長沒來掩護的話就真的危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 在這樣狹小的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而會礙他的手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就交給宗次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙…簡直就是野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙真的是…和宗大人一樣的武士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(898,670)}Samurai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天眼通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗次的口傳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防禦的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據宗次說 是觀察空中軌跡的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 依舊沒有餘裕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換作平時的話 肯定不會用刀擋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是藉機反擊或者避開去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:17:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局長！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:17:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加給宗次的障壁被打飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明能頂住20%HP的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個狀態的話估計挺不久的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要考慮撤退了……但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果逃錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺人鬼可能會轉變矛頭去攻擊大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有宗次自己就能壓住他勢頭的保證
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38}聖誕節過後的生意該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38}你還要換副職？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38}唉？這麼精美的禮物 真的可以收下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38}聖誕節快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險！宗次！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城惠那的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,極速一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}AccelFang
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是曉小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱形劍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}StealthBlade
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快速突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}QuickAssault
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆發步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}GustStep
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 如果沒有障壁的話 就被剛才那下幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 而且 那把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你問我為何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒他並不等同於解決問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背刺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}Assassinate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我沒有在此之上的技巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能點頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退！薺！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在工會會館等您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然去看同伴了？在這激戰之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盤算著如何牽制對手 看準時機開溜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知沒有勝算 但還為了同伴……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟這是平安夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要有點前輩的後輩的樣子 送點禮物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 我能說的卻沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神刀·狐鴉丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用心觀察 側耳傾聽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強烈祈望 為此而不斷思考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永不言棄 不懈鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然真的是表達不清到有點慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是 口傳的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還什麼都沒有抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明 要抓住什麼了的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種的 不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:22:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天在你們之間是要這麼相互問候的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼呢 主君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主君……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.64,0:24:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幻覺城市中彷徨的曉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.94,0:24:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展現在面前的 是後悔還是留在心底的舊傷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在迷茫 逃竄的她最終到達的月光海灘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有著令人懷念的溫暖——城惠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.72,0:24:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在死之世界中相逢的二人 各自心懷什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下話 黎明的迷子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇往直前吧 再一次
